summary: This script uses wget to download the repositories of GitHub users into separate log files. It retrieves the repositories for jiaxiaogang, Brethland, commaai (pages 1-3), and opennars.

details.comment: This script uses wget to download the repositories of GitHub users into separate log files. It retrieves the repositories for jiaxiaogang, Brethland, commaai (pages 1-3), and opennars.
details.content:
#!/bin/bash
wget 'https://github.com/jiaxiaogang?tab=repositories' -O 0_.log
wget 'https://github.com/Brethland?tab=repositories' -O 1_.log
wget 'https://github.com/commaai?page=1&tab=repositories' -O 2_.log
wget 'https://github.com/commaai?page=2&tab=repositories' -O 3_.log
wget 'https://github.com/commaai?page=3&tab=repositories' -O 4_.log
wget 'https://github.com/opennars?tab=repositories' -O 5_.log
